land.BeforeYouStart.p1                                                              = In this section, you need to tell us about the land or property being purchased.
land.BeforeYouStart.p2                                                              = We will ask for:
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet1                                                         = the type of property
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet2                                                         = whether an interest is being transferred or created
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet3                                                         = the address of the land or property
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet4                                                         = the local authority code
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet5                                                         = whether you’ll be sending plans by post
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet6                                                         = any minerals or mineral rights
land.BeforeYouStart.p3                                                              = You can also provide:
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet7                                                         = a title or folio number
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet8                                                         = an NLPG UPRN
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet9                                                         = if the transaction involves agricultural or developmental land
land.BeforeYouStart.bullet10                                                        = the area of the land

land.landTypeOfProperty.heading                                                     = What is the type of property?
land.landTypeOfProperty.01                                                          = 01 - Residential
land.landTypeOfProperty.01.hintText                                                 = A building used, suitable for use, or being constructed as a dwelling, including the garden, grounds and any right of way
land.landTypeOfProperty.02                                                          = 02 - Mixed
land.landTypeOfProperty.02.hintText                                                 = Where part of the property is residential
land.landTypeOfProperty.03                                                          = 03 - Non-residential
land.landTypeOfProperty.03.hintText                                                 = Where the whole property is non-residential
land.landTypeOfProperty.04                                                          = 04 - Additional residential property liable to higher rate
land.landTypeOfProperty.04.hintText                                                 = Where the purchaser owns more than one residential property at any one time
land.landTypeOfProperty.checkYourAnswersLabel                                       = Type of property
land.landTypeOfProperty.error.required                                              = Please select an option
land.landTypeOfProperty.change.hidden                                               = Type of property
land.checkYourAnswers.landTypeOfProperty.missing                                    = Select type of property

land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.title                                         = Interest transferred or created - About the land
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.heading                                       = Interest transferred or created
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.p1                                            = Interest is transferred when an existing interest in a property is moved from one party to another, like the transfer of freehold, beneficial rights or the assignment of an existing lease.
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.p2                                            = Interest is created when a new right or share in the property is established for a new party, like the grant of a new lease, taking on a debt, or the creation of an easement such as right of way.
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.subheading                                    = Which option best describes the transaction?
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.FGS                                           = FG - Freehold (in Scotland ownership) subject to one or more leases each reserving a ground or nominal rent
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.FPO                                           = FP - Freehold with vacant possession
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.FPO.hintText                                  = In Scotland owner’s interest with vacant possession
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.FTF                                           = FT - Freehold subject to a lease or tenancy
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.FTF.hintText                                  = In Scotland owner’s interest subject to tenancy
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.LG                                            = LG - Long leasehold at a ground or nominal rent with vacant possession
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.LPT                                           = LP - A lease to an occupier or with vacant possession and not a ground rent or nominal rent
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.LPT.hintText                                  = In Scotland tenant’s interest
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.LT                                            = LT - Leasehold subject to leases to an occupier
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.OT                                            = OT - All other interests
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.checkYourAnswersLabel                         = Interest transferred or created
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.error.required                                = Select an option
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.change.hidden                                 = Interest transferred or created
land.landInterestTransferredOrCreated.missing                                       = Select interest transferred or created

land.landRegisteredHmRegistry.heading                                               = Is the land or property registered with HM Land Registry?
