land.landSendingPlanByPost.title                                                    = Sending a plan by post - About the land
land.landSendingPlanByPost.heading                                                  = Sending a plan by post
land.landSendingPlanByPost.subheading                                               = Will you be sending a plan by post?
land.landSendingPlanByPost.checkYourAnswersLabel                                    = Sending a plan by post
land.landSendingPlanByPost.error.required                                           = Select land sending plan by post
land.landSendingPlanByPost.change.hidden                                            = Sending a plan by post
land.landSendingPlanByPost.details.summary                                          = Sending your plan by post
land.landSendingPlanByPost.details.content1                                         = The plan should indicate the scale used or be endorsed as ‘Not to Scale’. It must also show the return’s reference number, a description of the land and the local authority code.
land.landSendingPlanByPost.details.content2                                         = Send the land or property plan to:
land.landSendingPlanByPost.details.content3                                         = BT Stamp Duty Land Tax<br>HM Revenue and Customs<br>BX9 1LT
land.landSendingPlanByPost.p                                                        = A plan is required for all transactions involving land that does not have a postal address or where a boundary needs defining.
land.landSendingPlanByPost.missing                                                   = Select land sending plan by post

land.agriculturalOrDevelopmental.title                                              = Agricultural or developmental land
land.agriculturalOrDevelopmental.heading                                            = Agricultural or developmental land
land.agriculturalOrDevelopmental.subHeading                                         = Does the transaction involve agricultural or developmental land?
land.agriculturalOrDevelopmental.p1                                                 = Agricultural land refers to land primarily used for activities like farming, keeping livestock and horticulture. Developmental land refers to land with planning permission for a use other than agriculture.
land.agriculturalOrDevelopmental.checkYourAnswersLabel                              = Does the transaction involve agricultural or developmental land?
land.agriculturalOrDevelopmental.error.required                                     = Select yes if the transaction involves agricultural or developmental land
land.agriculturalOrDevelopmental.change.hidden                                      = if the transaction involves agricultural or developmental land
land.agriculturalOrDevelopmental.missing                                            = Select if the transaction involves agricultural or developmental land

