transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.error.maximum                     = The total consideration in money or money’s worth must be less than £9,999,999,999
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.error.totalConsideration          = The total consideration in money or money’s worth of all transactions must be more than the total consideration of a single transaction
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.change.hidden                     = Total consideration of all linked transactions
transaction.totalConsiderationOfLinkedTransaction.missing                           = Enter the total consideration of all linked transactions

